{
  "text": "In contrast to the findings in striatum, the expression of BDNF in juvenile rat PFC was lower than in their adult counterparts. A dopaminergic mechanism underlying these age-dependent differences is difficult to elucidate given that extracellular dopamine levels within the PFC appear to remain relatively consistent across ages [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
